            "body": "That's a good idea, just one more thing to consider though, are you sure there isn't a case when it would be useful to know the presence of a block nearby before/after performing certain actions?\r\n\r\nI'm thinking of something like when you try to use a bed and there are mobs nearby and the client doesn't let you do that, of course mobs are entities and not blocks but you see what I mean..\r\n\r\nIn that case a reusable function would be useful, and we might as well expose it as part of the API\r\n",
